  "text": "At this point, we have a total of 3R classes arriving to node 1 on subsystem 3, 2R classes overflowing from node 1 of subsystem 2, and R classes of local Poisson traffic. The node is analyzed using (7), [CITATION_1] , and (9). The algorithm then shifts to node 2.",
